Class Character

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Thread
      • main.java.questfortheabodeth.characters.Character
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable, Collidable, org.jsfml.graphics.Drawable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Enemy, Player

    public abstract class Character
extends java.lang.Thread
implements org.jsfml.graphics.Drawable, Collidable
    An abstract class to define all the common attributes that both the Player and all Enemy objects will have
